76561198019035889,Recommended,537860,26078355,"Posted: 16 October, 2016",all,bassaly,"I bought this game for 0,59 bucks, which in fact is not cheap for a product of such quality. Anyway I enjoyed playing it because I managed to finish all 10 levels in less than one hour. I cheated, of course. But hell, who would play this regularyly?There are a few things I really liked about this game, because they made me laugh:- There is an anti aircraft gun, but there are no aircrafts. At least I did not notice any, but maybe I overlooked them. Still this gun works fine against all other enemies.- Guns simply miss their targets. This is really innovative, I have never seen this on a tower defense game.- The graphics are said to be 'old style'. This redefines 'old'. I thought C64 was old, but obviously I was wrong.Compared to Android games, that can give you good value for 59 Cents, this one falls apart. But still I recommend buying it. I am serious. First (as stated) it is funny how ugly a game can be. Secondly, as long as you buy it in a special offer (like I did) this is the cheapest way of saving 40 Cents.And finally: No matter if you cheat or not: This is a tower defense game. So you can have at least a little fun with it.Go for it, just to support the silly fun!"
